Hi Manny! I love your videos so much but they're unfortunately a bit inaccessible -- would you mind captioning them, like you used to? Auto-generated captions aren't accurate, so proper captions are the only way to make videos accessible to those of us who need it (Deaf/Hoh people, people with sensory issues, etc.).

You could even open up community contribution captions so viewers could help with captioning, if you don’t have the time! I know personally, I help caption creators’ videos whenever I’m able, so I’m certain that many others would be willing as well. Thank you!
